" Increment number.
" As usual you can press '.' to repeat this action again.
nnoremap <leader>n+    <C-a>
vnoremap <leader>n+    <Esc><C-a>
nnoremap <leader>n=    <C-a>
vnoremap <leader>n=    <Esc><C-a>

" Decrement number.
" As usual you can press '.' to repeat this action again.
nnoremap <leader>n-    <C-x>
vnoremap <leader>n-    <Esc><C-x>
